thread.title: Treasury to Sell $90 Billion in Debt

author: wsjcom
title: Treasury to Sell $90 Billion in Debt
text:
The U.S. Treasury Department will auction $90 billion in securities next week. Details (all with minimum denominations of $100):
Monday: $48 billion in 13-week bills, a reopening of an issue first sold on Jan. 4, 2018, maturing July 5, 2018. Cusip number: 912796PN3.
